        "beatType": "motion_graphics",
        "startFrame": 474,
        "endFrame": 963,
        "componentPath": "src/visuals/Generated_VariableRewardScheduling.tsx",
        "transcriptSegment": "Notifications exploit a psychological mechanism called variable reward scheduling. It's the same principle behind slot machines. You never know if the next buzz will be something exciting or completely worthless. That unpredictability is what makes it addictive.",
